UID:Hv0SfghVXetAVEqk6jx9I
SUMMARY:How to Lose a Guy in 10 Days
DTSTAMP:20260701T101451Z
DTSTART:20260708T191500Z
DESCRIPTION:By midweek\, we could all use a little pick-me-up. Wine Wednesd
	ays are your perfect excuse to press pause on your problems and pour a gla
	ss instead. Each ticket includes a complimentary glass of house wine&mdash
	\;so you can toast being halfway to the weekend with friends (or a very go
	od date). Then sink into our ultra-comfortable seats and enjoy a fan-favor
	ite film under the stars. Midweek meltdown? Best handled with a movie. 🍷🎬\
	n\nhttps://rooftopcinemaclub.com/us/houston/uptown/screenings/how-to-lose-
